        "type": "markdown",
        "id": "7e579eb185f45054",
        "text": "The purpose of any system is the most important issue. The purpose determines the structure. The structure determines the roles. People fill the predetermined roles. Change the purpose. Don't try to change the people or minds until you have changed the purpose--in this case from profit taking to human wellbeing and neighborhood wellbeing."
